title: The Truth Untold.
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2u9iX9z

by JinForLife

5 years after their disbandment
BTS meets again for their band members’ wedding.
some logistics- BTS disbanded in 2025 and went on to pursue their solo careers.
Namjin is getting married in 2030- 5 years after their disbandment and after doing their own work
Jin nd Tae are renowned actors and their Drama OSTs are mostly sung by them. They worked together on two dramas, otherwise they have their solo porjects mostly.
Hobi became a well known choreographer, Namjoon and Yoongi became well known as producers- sometimes there three collab and release a rap song here and there. they are the reason for new successful groups in kpop.
Jimin and Jungkook both remained under the spot light but as super successful solo acts- collaborating with their rapper hyungs on their albums. and incidents led them to be open rivals in the industry, with people being utterly confused as to why they were suddenly so hateful.
all of them are award winners.
